data.description: GORGEOUS HOME FOR SALE WITH LAKE VIEWS!! This home in Gun Barrel City, TX, is in a superb location with close access to Cedar Creek Reservoir and a lovely lake view from the covered front porch. Home offers a delightful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, dual sinks, and granite countertops. The kitchen seamlessly connects to a breakfast nook, perfect for casual dining. The owner's suite is designed for comfort and convenience, offering his-and-hers closets and an ensuite bath with double sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Two additional bedrooms, one including a walk-in closet, share a full bathroom. Step outside to the spacious private backyard enclosed by wood fencing.  Furthermore, the neighborhood offers easy access to plenty of shopping and dining options. HUGE BUYER INCENTIVE, SELLER OFFERING $10K TOWARDS CLOSNG COSTS OR RATE TO BUY DOWN!! You don't want to miss out on the serenity and charm of this Gun Barrel City property, MAKE IT YOURS TODAY!!!
